9 summer looks pairing shorts with sweaters 〰️ I seem to be repeating this combination lately with my favorite basics both for everyday life and evenings. We have plenty of summer left in the season but it’s also an easy outfit as the weather starts to turn towards fall. ☀️ 

What’s your favorite, 1-9? 

1. Striped sweater with tailored shorts and Chanel flats. A classic, “dressed up” look for lunch on a cooler day. 
2. Denim shorts with oversized cardigan and Chanel flats. 
3. Lady sweater jacket paired with tailored shorts. 
4. Same striped sweater dressed down with linen shorts and flip flops. 
5. White cotton shorts paired with white sweatshirt-style sweater. 
6. White denim shorts paired with white tee and topped with oversized cardigan. 
7. White denim shorts paired with white tee + striped sweater over the shoulders. 
8. Grey oversized sweater sweater paired with denim shorts and sandals. 
9. Cream button-up sweater paired with linen shorts and cognac accessories.

The person who sent you this wants to have a magical holiday evening in wine country with you. 🎄🕊️✨

If you’re visiting Napa Valley, don’t miss a trip to @meritageresort to experience Merry Meritage—a winter wonderland in wine country. Enjoy the ice skating rink surrounded by fire pits for roasting marshmallows or the igloos for a cozy or intimate dining experience. Santa is there for storytime on the weekends and the flurry of faux snow was my personal favorite—the perfect way to end our evening and baby’s first *snow*! 🤣 ❄️ Great for a Napa day trip with or without kids or a little wine country staycation this holiday season! 🕊️

Have you been to Napa during the holidays? 🎄
